            "y1": 1438,
            "x2": 1498,
            "y2": 1583
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 12,
        "text": "तस्मादेतानिब्रह्मैव भवतीत्यवधारयेत् ।। ४९ ।।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_11_textline_12.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 259,
            "y1": 1559,
            "x2": 1791,
            "y2": 1726
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 13,
        "text": "ब्रह्महि कारण जगको जानो । ताबिन कोई और न मानो ।।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_11_textline_13.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 232,
            "y1": 1782,
            "x2": 1903,
            "y2": 1949
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 14,
        "text": "ताते यह प्रपंच सबजोई । ब्रह्महि है नहिं और जु कोई ४५",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_11_textline_14.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 138,
            "y1": 1921,
            "x2": 1903,
            "y2": 2065
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 15,
        "text": "व्याप्य औ व्यापक मिथ्या जानौ । सर्बमात्म इमि बचन सु-",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_11_textline_15.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 141,
            "y1": 2042,
            "x2": 1909,
            "y2": 2190
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 16,
        "text": "मानौ ।। ऐसे जान्यौ परम तत्त्व जब । भेद बुद्धि फिर कहों कहां",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_11_textline_16.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 129,
            "y1": 2160,
            "x2": 1915,
            "y2": 2301
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 17,
        "text": "तब ४६ निज मुख निश्चय करिके जोई । श्रुति ना तत्त्वनिवा-",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_11_textline_17.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 126,
            "y1": 2287,
            "x2": 1912,
            "y2": 2415
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 18,
        "text": "स्योसोई ।। कैसे द्वैत भासहै तबै । अद्वय ब्रह्म भयोथिर जबै ४७",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_11_textline_18.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 135,
            "y1": 2402,
            "x2": 1903,
            "y2": 2533
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 19,
        "text": "भेद दृष्टि श्रुति बिहित सुजानि । जन्म मरण तेहि होतहै मानि ।।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_11_textline_19.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 135,
            "y1": 2517,
            "x2": 1912,
            "y2": 2655
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 20,
        "text": "यह नानत्व बिलोकै जोई । माया करि वंचित नर सोई ।।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_11_textline_20.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 141,
            "y1": 2643,
            "x2": 1909,
            "y2": 2772
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 21,
        "text": "४८ परमात्मा अरु ब्रह्म सुजोई । सर्ब भूत ताते भये सोई ।।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_11_textline_21.png",
